  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834795864-DNIZBQEP9W065OO707TZ/1a-Pipsticks%2BSticker%2BSubscription%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I don't know about you but I have always been a fan of stickers. Puffy stickers, letter stickers, scratch and sniff stickers... you name it, I love it! Luckily, the apple didn't fall too far from the tree as Jack is equally as obsessed.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1b-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834850784-N4HIOA4QS27REDM8BSEF/1b-Pipsticks%2BSticker%2BSubscription%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1c-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834850541-3KIJ6GB7NQTTSQIQZACC/1c-Pipsticks%2BSticker%2BSubscription%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>This is why are both such big fans of <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=827689&amp;U=530666&amp;M=63829&amp;urllink=\">Pipsticks</a> sticker subscription! Each month we get the cutest vellum envelopes packed with various stickers and the two of us have the best time going through each and every sheet.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1d-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834891615-1O0139EEDI7OGLDR8O4F/1d-Pipsticks%2BSticker%2BSubscription%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1e-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834891229-8C7BVKVNW6213KY50M3O/1e-Pipsticks%2BSticker%2BSubscription%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Each month's pack includes a postcard and Jack always takes his time carefully choosing the best stickers for embellishing. He told me that this particular postcard would be sent to his new baby cousin, Jake.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834932475-2JSFP1DFB2LCREXBK8Z1/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com\">Ann-Marie</a>'s adorable son, Landon, was even there to supervise. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834958228-P6WUQX1ZFQJBJ0Q9504E/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I love supporting small businesses and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=827689&amp;U=530666&amp;M=63829&amp;urllink=\">Pipsticks</a> is just about the coolest concept for stationery lovers like myself and Jack. Be sure to check them out!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}